# Planning gate

For any task touching 2 or more files:

1. Run Phase 1 research first — reference `docs/8. agents/cursor-plan/1-research.md` or `@cursor-plan phase=1`
2. Present the research report and wait for confirmation before planning
3. Run Phase 2 synthesis — reference `docs/8. agents/cursor-plan/2-synthesis.md` or `@cursor-plan phase=2`
4. Present the plan and wait for explicit approval before writing any code
5. Only then implement, one step at a time — reference `docs/8. agents/cursor-plan/3-implementation.md`

Do not write code before the plan is confirmed. If the task is ambiguous, ask one clarifying question before starting research.

Single-file tasks and typo/config fixes are exempt.
